#      THE HANDLING OF FAILURE RETURNS DESERVES SPECIAL COMMENT.
#      THE LOCATION FLPTR CONTAINS THE POINTER TO THE LOCATION
#      ON THE MAIN STACK WHICH CONTAINS THE FAILURE RETURN
