#      CODE BLOCK (CDBLK OR EXBLK). WHEN A FAILURE OCCURS, THE
#      STACK IS POPPED AS INDICATED BY THE SETTING OF FLPTR AND
#      CONTROL IS PASSED TO THE APPROPRIATE LOCATION IN THE
