#      COLLECTION EXCEPT AT SUCH TIMES AS CONTENTS OF XL, XR
#      AND THE STACK ARE +CLEAN+ (SEE COMMENT BEFORE UTILITY
#      PROCEDURES AND IN GBCOL FOR MORE DETAIL). NOTE
