#      OF MEMORY TO FREE SPACE). SPITBOL PROCS WHICH CALL
#      SYSTEM ROUTINES ASSUME THAT THEY CANNOT PRECIPITATE
#      COLLECTION AND THIS MUST BE RESPECTED.
                            #} EJC
