#
#      TRAP BLOCK (CONTINUED)
#
#      VARIABLE INPUT ASSOCIATION
#
#           THE VALUE FIELD OF THE VARIABLE POINTS TO A TRBLK
#           INSTEAD OF CONTAINING THE DATA VALUE. IN THE CASE
