#      (WA)                  FIRST WORD OF BLOCK
#      (XR)                  POINTER TO BLOCK
#      JSR  BLKLN            CALL TO GET BLOCK LENGTH
#      (WA)                  LENGTH OF BLOCK IN BYTES
