#      BLKLN IS USED BY THE GARBAGE COLLECTOR AND IS NOT
#      PERMITTED TO CALL GBCOL DIRECTLY OR INDIRECTLY.
#
#      THE FIRST WORD STORED IN THE BLOCK (I.E. AT XR) MAY
#      BE ANYTHING, BUT THE CONTENTS OF WA MUST BE CORRECT.
