#
#      PRTNL -- PRINT NEW LINE (END PRINT LINE)
#
#      PRTNL PRINTS THE CONTENTS OF THE PRINT BUFFER, RESETS
#      THE BUFFER TO ALL BLANKS AND RESETS THE PRINT POINTER.
